Timothy Blake https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timothy_Blake 0 Timothy Blake is an actress whose career was active from the mid-1960s until the late 1990s. The films she has appeared in include, Adam at 6 A.M., They Went That-A-Way That-A-Way , Who'll Stop the Rain, and Finders Keepers. She has also appeared in television shows such as The Ropers.
